      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine, showroom-quality condition, reflecting a level of care that borders on the obsessive. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior appointments, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every component has been meticulously inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for mechanical and aesthetic perfection. This is a definitive acquisition for those who demand nothing less than the absolute best.",
