    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that remains in peak operational spec. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout the suspension geometry. Power is managed via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and delivered through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Rod bearings have been proactively addressed, and the valvetrain is perfectly shimmed. A mechanically flawless example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
