    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights the flawless body lines; you will find zero stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections across the entire surface. The original alloy wheels are pristine, free of any curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule\u2014the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the multi-zone climate control, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, document-backed service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is detailed to a professional standard, and the undercarriage remains remarkably clean, reflecting a life spent away from harsh elements. This is a collector-grade vehicle intended for a buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
